identification division.
program-id. Name Age.

data division.
   working-storage section.
   01  name        pic x(20).
   01  age         pic 9(3).

   procedure division.
         display "Enter your name: ".
         accept name.
         display "Enter your age: ".
         accept age.
         display "Hello, " name " you are " age " years old.".
         stop run.

   